{"id": "19070", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=19070", "title": "Onion", "text": "The is a &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20consumables\"&gt;consumable item&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nCharacteristics.\n is a consumable item which will heal 10 % of maximum Vitality and grant + 1 point to &lt;a href=\"Constitution\"&gt;Constitution&lt;/a&gt;. If character has &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Talents\"&gt;Five-Star Diner talent&lt;/a&gt; it will heal 20 % of maximum Vitality and grant + 2 points to &lt;a href=\"Constitution\"&gt;Constitution&lt;/a&gt;. The effect of last 3 turns.\nPoisoned is a consumable item that was poisoned through various means (either &lt;a href=\"Poison%20Bottle%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;poison bottle&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href=\"Zaikk%27s%20Talon\"&gt;Zaikk's Talon&lt;/a&gt;). Poisoning the will reduce its value to 0. Instead of healing it will deal poison damage equal to 10 % of the consumers maximum Vitality, rendering it unsafe for the living but safe for &lt;a href=\"Undead\"&gt;Undead&lt;/a&gt; and grant + 1 point to &lt;a href=\"Constitution\"&gt;Constitution&lt;/a&gt;. The effects last 3 turns.\nIf character has &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Talents\"&gt;Five-Star Diner talent&lt;/a&gt; the will deal poison damage equal to 20 % of the consumers maximum Vitality and grant + 2 points to &lt;a href=\"Constitution\"&gt;Constitution&lt;/a&gt;. The effects last 3 turns. \nLocations.\nTraders.\nFollowing NPCs sell a large variety of food and thus have a solid chance (not guaranteed) of having in their stock. Note that as a consumable item may be very randomly sold by other NPCs."}
{"id": "12427", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=12427", "title": "Onslaught", "text": "Onslaught is an &lt;a href=\"Warfare%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;expert Warfare&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Sourcery%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;source&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Skills\"&gt;skill&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nDescription.\nSkill.\nAttack 5 times with astonishing speed, each hit dealing damage based on the damage equipped weapon has.\nScroll and Skillbook.\n skillbook is a magical item that allows its reader to learn skill, if they have at least 3 points into &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Warfare\"&gt;Warfare&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Attributes%20and%20Abilities%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;ability&lt;/a&gt;, and use it indefinitely. In order to be able to cast the skill, character needs 2 free memory slots. Note that the book will disappear once read. The book weights 0.5 and its base value is 750 gold. Since is a expert Warfare skill, traders will start selling the skillbook once player character or their &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Companions\"&gt;companions&lt;/a&gt; reach level 13.\nSince is a weapon based skill and as such it does not have a scroll. It is also not possible to craft a skillbook.\nSkill Modifiers.\nScales off basic attack and gets a bonus from Strength, Finesse or Intelligence.\nLocations.\nTraders.\nFollowing table shows all NPCs who are guaranteed to sell warfare skillbooks, with their location and coordinates in the right column, from them. The location shown in the table (and the coordinates) are only for the initial location the NPC is in. Note that some of these may have other spell/skillbooks and goods to sell. &lt;a href=\"Gareth\"&gt;Gareth&lt;/a&gt; may follow the Godwoken on &lt;a href=\"The%20Lady%20Vengeance\"&gt;Lady Vengeance&lt;/a&gt; if his demands are met."}
