{"id": "6133", "revid": "49426621", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=6133", "title": "Orc Fight on the Beach", "text": " is a &lt;a href=\"Quests%20%28Original%20Sin%29\"&gt;side quest&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nDetailed Walkthrough.\nAfter crossing the bridge from &lt;a href=\"Cyseal%20beach\"&gt;Cyseal beach&lt;/a&gt; and following the ridge east, head down the slope to where three &lt;a href=\"legionaries\"&gt;legionaries&lt;/a&gt; are fighting a single &lt;a href=\"orc%20trooper\"&gt;orc trooper&lt;/a&gt;. As the party reaches the bottom of the slope on to the beach, an &lt;a href=\"orc\"&gt;orc&lt;/a&gt; ship will land on the beachhead, alongside a &lt;a href=\"Immaculates\"&gt;mysterious black figure&lt;/a&gt;. The &lt;a href=\"legionnaires\"&gt;legionnaires&lt;/a&gt; will then engage the landing party in combat and the Source Hunters will be drawn in. The mysterious figure and all orcs must be defeated before combat will end. If any/all of the legionaries fail to make it to the end of combat this will not affect the outcome, however, if they survive there is additional interaction with &lt;a href=\"Junius\"&gt;Junius&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Bibinus\"&gt;Bibinus&lt;/a&gt; back at the bridge."}
