{"id": "2620", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=2620", "title": "Ores", "text": "Ores are in \"\". They are required for a variety of &lt;a href=\"Weapons%20%28Dragon%20Knight%20Saga%29\"&gt;weapon&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Armour%20%28Dragon%20Knight%20Saga%29\"&gt;armour&lt;/a&gt;, and &lt;a href=\"jewelry\"&gt;jewelry&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Enchantments%2C%20Potions%20and%20Formulas\"&gt;enchantments&lt;/a&gt;, which can be preformed by &lt;a href=\"enchanter\"&gt;enchanter&lt;/a&gt;s.\nMining ore veins provides between one and seven units of ore. &lt;a href=\"Gems\"&gt;Gems&lt;/a&gt; can by procured, at random, by mining ore veins as well. Each type of ore vein can produce different types of gems (e.g. a Droxlerite vein can provide &lt;a href=\"Spinel\"&gt;Spinel&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href=\"Opal\"&gt;Opal&lt;/a&gt; gems).\nOres can also be obtained from the &lt;a href=\"Battle%20Tower\"&gt;Battle Tower&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"runners\"&gt;runners&lt;/a&gt;, merchants, as random loot, or as &lt;a href=\"Quests\"&gt;quest&lt;/a&gt; rewards.\n&lt;a href=\"Gold%20Ore\"&gt;Gold Ore&lt;/a&gt; is needed for all jewelry enchantments. &lt;a href=\"Venom%20Stone\"&gt;Venom Stone&lt;/a&gt; is needed for all poison enchantments.\nList of ores:"}
