{"id": "19662", "revid": "27868532", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=19662", "title": "Parchment (Ego Draconis)", "text": "Parchment is an &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Knight%20Saga%20Items\"&gt;item&lt;/a&gt; required for an unmarked quest involving &lt;a href=\"ZixZax\"&gt;ZixZax&lt;/a&gt;. He requires four pieces to decipher the writing.\nDescription.\nAll four parchments in &lt;a href=\"Broken%20Valley\"&gt;Broken Valley&lt;/a&gt; must be collected and brought to ZixZax to be translated. Bringing fewer than four results in him informing the player that it is impossible to decipher the text without all of them.\nUpon reading any of parchments, the following narrated text displays: . Each parchment has a unique word after that. The list of words is the following: , , and .\nAfter giving all of them to ZixZax, he will reveal that the words mean \"ancient\", \"poetics\", \"might\" and \"wise man\". He will then be reminded of the phrase and conclude that the parchments are all referring to &lt;a href=\"Bellegar\"&gt;Bellegar&lt;/a&gt;, as the creatures of the valley used to refer to him as these in the past.\nCompleting this allows the player to use \"Bellegar\" as a password for two teleporters in Broken Valley. One of them is slightly north of &lt;a href=\"Lovis%27%20Tower\"&gt;Lovis' Tower&lt;/a&gt; and the other is outside the &lt;a href=\"Old%20Cave\"&gt;old cave&lt;/a&gt;. The first one teleports the player to the very top of Lovis' Tower where they fight two level 12 &lt;a href=\"Ghost\"&gt;Lovis crawlers&lt;/a&gt; and can loot a chest with &lt;a href=\"charms\"&gt;charms&lt;/a&gt; and high rarity &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Knight%20Sage%20Weapons\"&gt;weapons&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20KNightr%20Saga%20Armour\"&gt;armour&lt;/a&gt;. The second teleporter brings the player to the outside of &lt;a href=\"Naberius%20Storage\"&gt;Naberius Storage&lt;/a&gt;, an area containing undead enemies, &lt;a href=\"droxlerite\"&gt;droxlerite&lt;/a&gt; veins and loot. To open the door &lt;a href=\"Naberius\"&gt;Naberius&lt;/a&gt; must also have been &lt;a href=\"Mindread\"&gt;Mindread&lt;/a&gt; to learn the password. It is possible to reach this area without the teleporter with good enough jumping around the mountain cliffs.\nLocations.\nThe four parchments can be found in Broken Valley in the following locations:"}
