{"id": "10843", "revid": "27868532", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=10843", "title": "Poison the Orcs' Water Supply", "text": "Poison the Orcs' water supply is a &lt;a href=\"Divine%20Divinity%20Quests\"&gt;side quest&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Divine%20Divinity\"&gt;Divine Divinity&lt;/a&gt;\"\nDetails Walkthrough.\nAfter speaking to &lt;a href=\"Captain%20Mitox\"&gt;Captain Mitox&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Lucian\"&gt;Lucian&lt;/a&gt; will be asked to breach the &lt;a href=\"orc\"&gt;orc&lt;/a&gt;'s camp and poison their water supply. It is possible, but highly dangerous to cross the battlefield to reach the camp and breach the entrance; however, there is an alternative path via the hatch in the buildings on the south side of the &lt;a href=\"destroyed%20village\"&gt;destroyed village&lt;/a&gt;. This path will take Lucian under the battlefield and leads out into the middle of the camp; it is not without danger, but the number of orc troops within are significantly less than those out on the battlefield.\nUpon exiting the shaft, one will be immediately set upon by orcs; however, if doing so at night the number of troops will be lesser. From here head south to find the well and drag/drop the poison on the well to taint it. Once done, return to Mitox through the underground path or over the battlefield."}
