{"id": "12395", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=12395", "title": "Poisonous Skin", "text": "Poisonous Skin is a &lt;a href=\"Geomancer%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;Geomancer&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Polymorph%20%28Skill%20Class%29\"&gt;Polymorph&lt;/a&gt; source skill in \"\".\nDescription.\nSkill.\n is a supportive mixed source skill that allows character to enchant their very skin with poison for 2 turns, thus granting them immunity to &lt;a href=\"Poisoned%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Poisoned&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Acid%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Acid&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Slowed%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Slowed&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Petrified%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Petrified&lt;/a&gt; status effects alongside increased Poison Resistance Earth Resistance and by 100 %. However this skill will also decrease Air Resistance by 30 %. When caster is directly damaged they will bleed poison (note that this excludes bleeding caused by &lt;a href=\"Flesh%20Sacrifice\"&gt;Flesh Sacrifice&lt;/a&gt;). \nSince this skill applies positive status effect it will always bypass armour.\nSince relies on &lt;a href=\"Geomancy\"&gt;Geomancy&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Metamorphosis\"&gt;Metamorphosis&lt;/a&gt; magic it cannot be cast if character is affected by &lt;a href=\"Silenced%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Silenced&lt;/a&gt; status effect.\nScroll and Skillbook.\n skillbook is a magical item that allows its reader to learn skill, if they have at least 2 points into both &lt;a href=\"Geomancer%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;Geomancer&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Polymorph\"&gt;Polymorph&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Attributes%20and%20Abilities%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;abilities&lt;/a&gt;, and use it indefinitely. In order to be able to cast the skill, character needs 2 free memory slots. Note that the book will disappear once read. The book weights 0.5 and its base value is 500 gold. A skillbook can be crafted by combining any &lt;a href=\"Geomancer%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;Geomancer&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Polymorph\"&gt;Polymorph&lt;/a&gt; skillbooks out of which atleast one must be a source skillbook. Since is a mixed source skill, traders do not have the skillbook for sale.\n is one of the few magic-based skills in the game that does not have a scroll.\nSkill Modifiers.\n is a supportive skill that provides clear set bonuses. As such these bonuses by themselves cannot be increased, however they can stack with other items, skills or talents that provide them.\nSince the AP cost to cast this skill is always 1 AP it cannot be lowered by any means.\nThe only way to improve this skill is to increase its range through skills or talents.\nLocations.\nTraders.\nThis skill cannot be bought or stolen from NPCs in the game."}
