{"id": "3962", "revid": "37013771", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=3962", "title": "Strange Volumes", "text": "Three books written by &lt;a href=\"Tim\"&gt;Tim&lt;/a&gt;, the &lt;a href=\"Black%20Boar\"&gt;Black Boar&lt;/a&gt;'s barkeep. Each volume contains a hint to find the next. Volumes cannot be skipped as they do not appear until the previous Volume has been read.\nFinding all of them will net the player a &lt;a href=\"Skill%20Book\"&gt;Skill Book&lt;/a&gt;.\nDetailed Walkthrough.\nThe &lt;a href=\"Strange%20Volume\"&gt;first&lt;/a&gt; volume can be located behind a level three locked door on the third floor.\nReading the first volume will cause the second volume to appear atop the bar on the first floor.\nReading the second volume will cause the third volume to appear on top of a pile of books on the second floor.\nAfter reading all three books a &lt;a href=\"Skill%20Book\"&gt;Skill Book&lt;/a&gt; will appear in the fireplace on the first floor."}
