{"id": "18309", "revid": "94812", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=18309", "title": "Straw", "text": " is a type of &lt;a href=\"Divine%20Divinity%20miscellaneous%20items\"&gt;miscellaneous item&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Divine%20Divinity\"&gt;Divine Divinity&lt;/a&gt;.\"\nCharacteristics.\nStraw can be combined to hay, to serve as bed, which can also be carried. Making hay is a simple process of combining two unfolded straws. Straws are unfolded by clicking on them.\nOnce created, hay can be carried in the inventory and used from there. If dropped however, it cannot be picked up again. Hay doesn't weigh anything.\nHay can sometimes be found as well.\nLocations.\nOften found in &lt;a href=\"The%20Farmlands\"&gt;The Farmlands&lt;/a&gt;."}
