{"id": "12439", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=12439", "title": "Summon Condor", "text": "Summon condor is a &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Summoning\"&gt;special Summoning skill&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nDescription.\nSkill.\nSummons a Condor to fight for you. The Condor has the ability to fly with &lt;a href=\"Flight\"&gt;Flight&lt;/a&gt; skill and two attack skills: &lt;a href=\"Peck\"&gt;Peck&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Gust\"&gt;Gust&lt;/a&gt;\nStats depends on casters Summoning &lt;a href=\"Attributes%20and%20Abilities%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;ability&lt;/a&gt;.\nGift Bag: Pet Power.\nGift bag: Pet Power allows the player to infuse not only their Incarnate but also all other summoned creatures. This includes \"Condor\" as well. Note that skills gained by infusing it, may differ from skills gained by infusing other summoned creatures."}
{"id": "3597", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=3597", "title": "Summon Demon", "text": "Summon Demon is a &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Knight%20Saga%20Skills%23Priest\"&gt;Priest skill&lt;/a&gt; that can be used by &lt;a href=\"the%20Dragon%20Knight\"&gt;the Dragon Knight&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nDescription.\nSummon Demon is a active Priest skill that allows the Knight to summon a &lt;a href=\"Demons\"&gt;Demon&lt;/a&gt; from hell. The Demon will follow and attack enemies as well as attract their attention. Each level increases the demon's damage, HP, resistances and spell power.\u00a0The exact amounts are not shown but a summoned creature is almost always able to win a one-on-one fight with a &lt;a href=\"Creatures\"&gt;monster&lt;/a&gt; of the same level."}
