{"id": "8314", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=8314", "title": "Sword of the Paladin", "text": "Sword of the Paladin is a &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Knight%20Saga%20Weapons%23Two-Handed%20Weapons\"&gt;special two-handed sword&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nLocation.\nSword of the Paladin is a special &lt;a href=\"Weapons%20%28Dragon%20Knight%20Saga%29\"&gt;weapon&lt;/a&gt; that can be acquired at &lt;a href=\"Bellegar\"&gt;Bellegar's&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Mysterious%20Cave%20/%20Morals%20Cave\"&gt;Morals Cave&lt;/a&gt; in the &lt;a href=\"Orobas%20Fjords\"&gt;Orobas Fjords&lt;/a&gt;. \nTo obtain it, the Dragon Knight must make all good choices in the cave (side with the woman, help the farmer, and help the dying man). In the final room, choose this weapon as your reward. Note that making all good choices requires you to sacrifice a point of Vitality, a point of Spirit, and a point of a random stat."}
