{"id": "19176", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=19176", "title": "Tea Herbs", "text": "The is a type of &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Consumables%23Food%20and%20Drink\"&gt;herb&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nCharacteristics.\nTea Herbs are a collection of herbs that grow on &lt;a href=\"Rivellon\"&gt;Rivellon&lt;/a&gt; and are primarily used in making tea. When consumed they will restore 5 % of Maximum Health. If character has &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Talents\"&gt;Five-Star Diner talent&lt;/a&gt; the herbs will restore 10 % of Maximum Health. \n\"Distinctive Tea Herbs are a rare collection of herbs which can only be grown from &lt;a href=\"Tea%20Leaf%20Seedling\"&gt;Tea Leaf Seedling&lt;/a&gt;s placed upon oil surface. When consumed they will restore 5 % of Maximum Health like its base counterpart. If character has &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Talents\"&gt;Five-Star Diner talent&lt;/a&gt; the herbs will restore 10 % of Maximum Health. Note that in order to grow these herbs and buy them the player must have activated Gift Bag: Herb Gardens\"'.\nLocations.\nTraders.\nFollowing NPCs sell a large variety of food and thus have a solid chance (not guaranteed) of having in their stock. Note that as a consumable item may be very randomly sold by other NPCs.\nUsage.\nFollowing table shows all items for which this item is used for. "}
