{"id": "6033", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=6033", "title": "Fire Absorption Shield", "text": ", also known as Fire Shield is a &lt;a href=\"Pyrokinetic%20%28Original%20Sin%29\"&gt;Pyrokinetic spell&lt;/a&gt; in ' and '. \nOriginal Sin.\nDescription.\nEnchant self or ally with a fire shield that absorbs X damage from all sources (not only fire). Does not stack with other elemental shield spells with 100% base chance to set spells.\n100% base chance. The shield breaks early if the damage absorption is exceeded.\nEnhanced Edition.\nDescription.\nEnchant self or ally with a fire shield. A fire shield absorbs fire damage until it breaks.\nImmune to the Burning status. \nDuration: 3 turns. \nWater Resistance: -25% \nRange: 15.0m"}
