{"id": "17789", "revid": "31775388", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=17789", "title": "Firewater", "text": " is a mercenary of &lt;a href=\"the%20Lone%20Wolves\"&gt;the Lone Wolves&lt;/a&gt; residing at &lt;a href=\"Cullwoods%20Mill\"&gt;Cullwoods Mill&lt;/a&gt; in 1242 AD.\nBackground.\nFirewater is a mercenary of the Lone Wolves, haunted by his girlfriend &lt;a href=\"Edie%20Engrym\"&gt;Edie Engrym&lt;/a&gt;, who was murdered by him in order to be accepted to the Lone Wolves. He can be found guarding the main entrance to the mill, just above &lt;a href=\"Pigsbane\"&gt;Pigsbane&lt;/a&gt;."}
{"id": "17951", "revid": "27868532", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=17951", "title": "Fireworks", "text": " is a &lt;a href=\"Divine%20Divinity%20quests\"&gt;side quest&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Divine%20Divinity\"&gt;Divine Divinity&lt;/a&gt;\". One may get directed to this quest either by &lt;a href=\"Corinna\"&gt;Corinna&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Kyrinil\"&gt;Kyrinil&lt;/a&gt;, or simply by going into &lt;a href=\"Anthrabert\"&gt;Anthrabert's&lt;/a&gt; room in &lt;a href=\"Ducal%20Inn\"&gt;Ducal Inn&lt;/a&gt;.\nDetailed Walkthrough.\nFor reasons unknown, &lt;a href=\"Anthrabert\"&gt;Anthrabert&lt;/a&gt; wants &lt;a href=\"Mpenzak\"&gt;Mpenzak's&lt;/a&gt; cart to be burnt. He suggests to do this task while Mpenzak is in the bar, by destroying the lamp on his cart. Doing this and returning back to Anthrabert completes the quest.\nDepending how this quest is obtained, rewards differ bit; \nIts possible to get both rewards by first doing money reward route, and then asking Anthrabert for a bottle of wine, which he will give freely as an additional reward for dealing with the Mpenzak situation so well.\nIf initially rejecting the offer, it's possible to miss this quest and potentially breaking the &lt;a href=\"A%20Bottle%20of%20Wine\"&gt;A Bottle of Wine&lt;/a&gt; quest. After a while somebody else will have already burnt the cart down."}
