{"id": "5552", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=5552", "title": "Flare", "text": " is a &lt;a href=\"Pyrokinetic%20%28Original%20Sin%29\"&gt;Pyrokinetic spell&lt;/a&gt; in ' and '.\nOriginal Sin.\nDescription.\nCast magical heat that does X-Y fire damage. \n100% base chance to set &amp; \nCan burn targets that are already warm. Can target terrain to create a fire surface, burn ooze, evaporate water, or melt ice.\nEnhanced Edition.\nDescription.\nCast a magical heat that does X-Y fire damage.\n100% chance to set Warm status for 3 turns.\nWarm makes target a bit less resistance to fire spells but more resistant to water spells. \nCan burn targets that are already warm. \nCan target terrain to create fire surface, burn ooze or oil, evaporate water, or melt ice. Can explode some clouds."}
