{"id": "2066", "revid": "31775388", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=2066", "title": "Folo", "text": "Folo is the pig farmer at &lt;a href=\"Broken%20Valley%20Village\"&gt;Broken Valley Village&lt;/a&gt;. He is located in the fenced area outside of &lt;a href=\"Folo%27s%20House\"&gt;Folo's House&lt;/a&gt;. Following the assault on Broken Valley, he migrates to &lt;a href=\"Aleroth\"&gt;Aleroth&lt;/a&gt;.\nBackground.\nFolo is the resident pig farmer of Broken Valley and when the Dragon Knight first arrives at the village, he is lamenting the fact that his favourite pig, &lt;a href=\"Kevin\"&gt;Kevin&lt;/a&gt; has been sent to &lt;a href=\"Jackson%27s%20Farm\"&gt;Jackson's Farm&lt;/a&gt; to be transported to &lt;a href=\"Rivertown\"&gt;Rivertown&lt;/a&gt; as rations. His love of pigs is so great that he had the pig Bessy buried with full burial rite in the &lt;a href=\"chapel\"&gt;chapel&lt;/a&gt;'s graveyard.\nFollowing &lt;a href=\"Damian\"&gt;Damian&lt;/a&gt;'s invasion of Broken Valley, he and Kevin escape to Aleroth to meet the same fate would have if he remained. Murdered by the zombie &lt;a href=\"Zombie%20Jake\"&gt;Jake&lt;/a&gt;, his corpse is used in a ritual to grant the long term, undead resident invincibility. This results in him having be murdered a second time by Kevin's saviour in order for the zombie's reign to end."}
