{"id": "11386", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=11386", "title": "Global Cooling", "text": " is an &lt;a href=\"Hydrosophist%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;adept Hydrosophist&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Skills\"&gt;skill&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nDescription.\nSkill.\n is an offensive hydrosophist skill that allows character to release a wave of cold around themselves. This wave deals water damage to all enemies in 13 meter radius from the caster. This skill will also freeze all water and blood surfaces as well as erase their cloud counterparts. Alongside freezing susceptible surfaces in range it will also douse all fire surfaces and clouds. This skill will also douse all blessed fire surfaces and clouds but do nothing against cursed fire surfaces and clouds. \nCharacters without Magic Armour will be afflicted with &lt;a href=\"Chilled%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Chilled&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href=\"Frozen%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Frozen&lt;/a&gt; (if target is already affected by &lt;a href=\"Wet%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Wet&lt;/a&gt; or Chilled) status effects for 2 turns and suffer damage directly to their health. Due to this skill dealing area of effect damage around the caster it will most likely reveal all hostile characters under &lt;a href=\"Invisible%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Invisible&lt;/a&gt; status effect in 13 meter radius from the caster.\nSince relies on &lt;a href=\"Hydrosophy\"&gt;Hydrosophy&lt;/a&gt; magic it cannot be cast if caster is affected by &lt;a href=\"Silenced%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Silenced&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Enraged%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Enraged&lt;/a&gt; status effects. skill is not reflected back when the target is under &lt;a href=\"Deflective%20Barrier\"&gt;Deflective Barrier&lt;/a&gt; skill (Definitive Edition only).\nScroll and Skillbook.\n skillbook is a magical item that allows its reader to learn skill, if they have at least 2 points into &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Hydrosophist\"&gt;Hydrosophist&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Attributes%20and%20Abilities%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;ability&lt;/a&gt;, and use it indefinitely. In order to be able to cast the skill, character needs 1 free memory slot. Note that the book will disappear once read. The book weights 0.5 and its base value is 500 gold. A skillbook can be crafted if a scroll is combined with a &lt;a href=\"Blank%20Water%20Skillbook\"&gt;Blank Water Skillbook&lt;/a&gt;. Since is an adept Hydrosophist skill, traders will start selling the skillbook once &lt;a href=\"Godwoken\"&gt;Godwoken&lt;/a&gt; reach level 9.\n is one of the few magic-based skills in the game that does not have a scroll.\nSkill Modifiers.\nDamage of this skill is calculated with the following formula: (Base Damage) x (1 + Elemental Bonus%) x (1 + Attribute Bonus% + Weapon Skill Bonus %) x (1 + High Ground Bonus% + Crit Bonus%) x ( 1 + Misc Bonus %)\nThe damage of this skill is affected by the following attributes of the caster:\nOut of these the most effect on the damage have Level and then Hydrosophist ability as the latter increases damage by 5 % per point. Level provides greatest boost to the damage done. Intelligence provides the lowest bonus out of the three (3 points in Intelligence are equal to 1 point of Hydrosophist).\nWhen it comes to enemies they may resist water damage if they have: Water Immunity Status and high enough Water Resistance (which lowers water damage done).\n properties can be affected by talents, consumable items (some of which may be affected by &lt;a href=\"Five-Star%20Diner%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;Five-Star Diner&lt;/a&gt; talent) and other skills.\nLocations.\nTraders.\nFollowing table shows all NPCs who are guaranteed to sell hydrosophist spellbooks, with their location and coordinates in the right column, from them. The location shown in the table (and the coordinates) are only for the initial location the NPC is in. Note that some of these may have other spell/skillbooks and goods to sell. &lt;a href=\"Almira\"&gt;Almira&lt;/a&gt; may follow the Godwoken on &lt;a href=\"The%20Lady%20Vengeance\"&gt;Lady Vengeance&lt;/a&gt; if her demands are met. Also note that &lt;a href=\"Lizard%20Dreamer\"&gt;Lizard Dreamer&lt;/a&gt; requires a persuasion check to be passed in order to speak with him, otherwise he (and the whole encampment) will turn hostile. "}
