{"id": "12223", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=12223", "title": "Guardian Angel", "text": "Guardian Angel is a &lt;a href=\"Warfare%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;master Warfare&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Skills\"&gt;skill&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nDescription.\nSkill.\nAllies in melee range redirect 50% of received damage to you.\nScroll and Skillbook.\n skillbook is a magical item that allows its reader to learn skill, if they have at least 3 points into &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Warfare\"&gt;Warfare&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Attributes%20and%20Abilities%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;ability&lt;/a&gt;, and use it indefinitely. In order to be able to cast the skill, character needs 1 free memory slot. Note that the book will disappear once read. The book weights 0.5 and its base value is 1400 gold. Since is a master Warfare skill, traders will start selling the skillbook once player character or their &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Companions\"&gt;companions&lt;/a&gt; reach level 16.\nSince is a weapon based skill and as such it does not have a scroll. It is also not possible to craft a skillbook.\nLocations.\nTraders.\nFollowing table shows all NPCs who are guaranteed to sell warfare skillbooks, with their location and coordinates in the right column, from them. The location shown in the table (and the coordinates) are only for the initial location the NPC is in. Note that some of these may have other spell/skillbooks and goods to sell. &lt;a href=\"Gareth\"&gt;Gareth&lt;/a&gt; may follow the Godwoken on &lt;a href=\"The%20Lady%20Vengeance\"&gt;Lady Vengeance&lt;/a&gt; if his demands are met."}
