{"id": "16935", "revid": "27868532", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=16935", "title": "The Mind Of...", "text": " is a &lt;a href=\"Ego%20Draconis%20quests\"&gt;side quest&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nDetailed walkthrough.\nThis quest is a side quest connected to the main quest &lt;a href=\"The%20Prophecy%20%28quest%29\"&gt;The Prophecy&lt;/a&gt;. The goal of this quest is to find out as much as possible about the candidates who will serve &lt;a href=\"the%20Dragon%20Knight\"&gt;the Dragon Knight&lt;/a&gt;. \nThis quest is divided into sub-quests. Each sub-quest is marked as completed (green) whenever the corresponding candidate has been mindread.\nThe Mind of Allan.\nAllan is a candidate for alchemist who made his own small camp in front of &lt;a href=\"Laiken%27s%20Study\"&gt;Laiken's Study&lt;/a&gt; which is next to &lt;a href=\"Sentinel%20Island\"&gt;Sea Side Shrine&lt;/a&gt;. To get there one needs to go past Wesson's camp then turn left. Allan's camp is surrounded by 8 level 16 Abomination's. \nAllan can be found walking and looking back every few moments. By speaking with him and mindreading him the quest is marked as completed.\nThe Mind of Barbatos.\nBarbatos is the second candidate for alchemist who can be found wandering on small beach within &lt;a href=\"Sentinel%20Island%20Encampment\"&gt;the Starbound encampment&lt;/a&gt;. He wears red robes and can be sometimes seen speaking with &lt;a href=\"Turgoyn\"&gt;Turgoyn&lt;/a&gt;. \nBy speaking and mindreading him the quest is marked as complete.\nThe Mind of Hermosa.\nHermosa is the candidate for Skill Trainer and a captain of the Starbound crew. She is found in the back of the &lt;a href=\"Sentinel%20Island%20Encampment\"&gt;the Starbound camp&lt;/a&gt; walking in and out of her private quarters. By speaking with her and mindreading her the quest is complete.\nThe Mind of Igor.\nIgor is a candidate for Necromancer and a servant of another candidate Jonelath. He is found in the back of the &lt;a href=\"Necromancer%20Cave\"&gt;Necromancer Cave&lt;/a&gt; which is in front of the Wesson's camp. Speaking with him and mindreading him will complete the quest.\nThe Mind of Jonelath.\nJonelath is the second candidate for the Necromancer and master of Igor. He is a Black Ring necromancer who along with Igor made their stand in the &lt;a href=\"Necromancer%20Cave\"&gt;Necromancer Cave&lt;/a&gt; which can be found near Wesson's camp. Upon entering the cave he will engage in conversation with the Knight. Mindreading him will complete the quest.\nThe Mind of Kenneth.\nKenneth is a Dragon Slayer and a second candidate for the Skill Trainer. He made his camp on the other side of the Sentinel Island, past &lt;a href=\"Sentinel%20Island%20Encampment\"&gt;the Starbound camp&lt;/a&gt;. Speaking with him and mindreading him will complete the quest. \nThe Mind of Radcliff.\nRadcliff is a candidate for Enchanter who resides within the &lt;a href=\"Sentinel%20Island%20Encampment\"&gt;the Starbound camp&lt;/a&gt; he can be found smithing in front of Hermosa's quarters. By speaking and mindreading him the quest is marked as complete.\nThe Mind of Wesson.\nWesson is a candidate for Enchanter and a husband of Ginny. He and his wife made a camp in front of the &lt;a href=\"Necromancer%20Cave\"&gt;Necromancer Cave&lt;/a&gt;, past the Sentinel Island Beach shrine.\nBy speaking and mindreading him the quest is marked as completed."}
